tric materials. This review presents a survey of a wide range of\nexperimental investigations of type-I clathrate compounds, together with a\nreview of theoretical interpretations of the peculiar thermal and dynamic\nproperties observed in these materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Feb 2014 09:09:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-06"}
